summary: Dual wielding living dead girl. Custom textured body. Found near the Hall of the Dead in Falkreath
descriptionHtml:
Where else but a graveyard in Falkreath? A strange looking woman can be found at all hours near the Hall of the Dead. The local priest of Arkay has spoken with her and has allowed her to stay. It seems that she's waiting for someone.


Fun Facts:
Level 6-80
Essential
Any Crime
